Package org.netbeans.swing.outline

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CheckRenderDataProvider
    An extension to RenderDataProvider adding a possibility to display a check box in the tree portion an Outline, next to the label.
    ExtTreeWillExpandListener
    A trivial extension to TreeWillExpandListener, to allow listeners to be notified if another TreeWillExpandListener vetoes a pending expansion.
    OutlineModel
    A model for an Outline ("tree-table").
    RenderDataProvider
    A class which can provide rendering data for the tree portion an Outline, such as converting values to text, providing tooltip text and icons.
    RowModel
    A model for the rows in an Outline.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultOutlineCellRenderer
    An outline-aware TableCellRenderer which knows how to paint expansion handles and indent child nodes an appropriate amount.
    DefaultOutlineModel
    Proxies a standard TreeModel and TableModel, translating events between the two.
    Outline
    An Outline, or tree-table component.
    TreePathSupport
    Manages expanded/collapsed paths for the Outline.
